{"tid":928392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職業拳擊轉業餘　翻譯：商業轉體育　曹星如：一直夢想做香港代表","createTime":"2018-12-04T20:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T00:03:23.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78b57c2c2e43cb15f79387759838103d2fff61e6","tid":928392,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:31:32.000Z","msg":"由於人們長期以來對直接身體對抗的拳擊存在認識上的差異，所以，拳擊運動至今仍流行著兩種不同形式的比賽&mdash;&mdash;業餘拳擊與職業拳擊。<br />\n<br />\n職業拳擊，從搏擊賺錢開始，所謂 prizefighting ，發展為 sports entertainment 。<br />\n<br />\n業餘拳擊，以鍛煉身體、提高運動技術水平和促進友誼為宗旨，一直朝著體育教育的道路前進和發展，以奧運為最高殿堂，又叫奧運拳擊。<br />\n<br />\n職業拳手是個人拳手。<br />\n<br />\n業餘拳手參加比賽是代表國家，代表一國的實力。或者代表學校，等等。<br />\n<br />\n職業拳擊賽事，職業拳手經由經理人找對戰對手，談出場費等，敲定合約，談成每一場賽事。<br />\n<br />\n業餘拳擊賽事，一般來說，是晉級淘汰制連環比賽，參賽無錢收，勝利了也只有獎牌，主辦機構不給獲獎運動員一分錢。<br />\n<br />\n職業拳手，須自負盈虧，自己花錢僱用教練、醫生與訓練人員。亦須由經理人安排賽事，籌劃拳擊生涯。世紀大戰 Mayweather VS Pacquiao ，兩人共得拳酬超過2億美元。不過，其實大部分職業拳手都是兼職，除靠比賽收入，通常有另外一份工作。<br />\n<br />\n業餘拳手，一般來說，收入來自所代表群體的權力機構。在台灣，政府給予國家訓練中心的選手月薪，負擔所有費用，業餘拳擊中的國手是全職的。有些國家，勝出比賽，政府會給獎金。所代表國的私人機構或財團也可能提供收入，例如馬會基金和恒基地產有獎勵計劃，在雅加達亞運獲得獎牌，有獎金。<br />\n<br />\n職業拳擊賽事，一場比賽回合數可以很多，在場上時間也長。1983年，美國的WBA輕量級拳王韋‧文仙尼在衛冕戰中於第14回合打死了韓國籍挑戰者金得九。兩個月後，金得九的老母因喪子悲傷過度，服毒自盡。世界拳擊組織在壓力下，拳王爭霸賽回合數減少至12回合。比賽中的相互頂撞、推壓、扭搶等等，雖然賽規有載明，但裁判都少有判罰。<br />\n<br />\n業餘拳擊賽事，一場比賽全場只有11分鐘，扣除回合之間休息後更少。同一回合三次進入被 KO 讀秒程序，輸，全場四次，輸。裁判嚴格執行比賽規則，任何違規行為都立即判罰，輕者警告、扣分，重者停止比賽或取消比賽資格。<br />\n<br />\n職業拳擊賽事，一般是一日賽事，賽前有幾個月時間針對約好的對手做訓練和想策略，賽後能長時間休養。<br />\n<br />\n業餘拳擊賽事，誰是對手，由在賽事中連日來的晉級淘汰制對戰賽結決定，賽事的對賽表在比賽舉行前數日才由賽會抽籤得出，充滿變數和未知。如果持續晉級，要數天內進行多場賽事，面對多個對手。<br />\n<br />\n由於本質不同，國際業餘拳擊聯合會規定，職業拳手不能參加業餘拳賽，而業餘拳手也不能參加有獎金的職業拳賽，如果參加，就意味他自動放棄業餘拳手身份。<br />\n<br />\n中國網上流傳，古巴著名拳擊運動員 Stevenson 和 Savon 受到古巴人民愛戴，甘願放棄來自美國職業拳壇的重金誘惑和個人發財的機會，終身以一名業餘拳手的資格代表古巴3次踏進奧運會賽場，3次為古巴摘取奧運會重量級拳擊金牌，而 Stevenson 對於受誘和拳王阿里來場世紀之戰的100萬美金，當時說了句名言：「100萬美元怎能與1000萬古巴人的榮耀相比！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsources:<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/sports/yag9kbg.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fsports%2Fyag9kbg.html&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=440aa28c\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/sports/yag9kbg.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/Project/2016Olympic/info-sports/222.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2FProject%2F2016Olympic%2Finfo-sports%2F222.aspx&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f05d7268\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/Project/2016Olympic/info-sports/222.aspx</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/Project/2016Olympic/info-athletes/88.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2FProject%2F2016Olympic%2Finfo-athletes%2F88.aspx&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3b5f3704\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/Project/2016Olympic/info-athletes/88.aspx</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/findboxing/posts/951915864950721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffindboxing%2Fposts%2F951915864950721%2F&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=861b0931\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/findboxing/posts/951915864950721/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/photos/a.580179058844498/581327138729690/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finboxinghk%2Fphotos%2Fa.580179058844498%2F581327138729690%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c0197e90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/photos/a.580179058844498/581327138729690/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/photos/a.580179058844498/580177115511359/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finboxinghk%2Fphotos%2Fa.580179058844498%2F580177115511359%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=471b3056\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/photos/a.580179058844498/580177115511359/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/photos/a.580179058844498/580179642177773/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finboxinghk%2Fphotos%2Fa.580179058844498%2F580179642177773%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f1e1a72b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/photos/a.580179058844498/580179642177773/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/posts/591826051013132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finboxinghk%2Fposts%2F591826051013132&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=68e598ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inboxinghk/posts/591826051013132</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/武備志/265700/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%AD%A6%E5%82%99%E5%BF%97%2F265700%2F&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=228a09c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/武備志/265700/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/武備志/266527/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%AD%A6%E5%82%99%E5%BF%97%2F266527%2F&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=17038128\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/武備志/266527/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ettoday.net/news/744208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F744208&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7562e4a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ettoday.net/news/744208</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20181201/s00006/1543564657103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20181201%2Fs00006%2F1543564657103%2F&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=0d0a443a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20181201%2Fs00006%2F1543564657103%2F&h=445b5bf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20181201/s00006/1543564657103/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20181130/s00006/1543591217580/【轉戰業餘】為奧運夢棄職業拳酬-曹星如不忘初心爭做香港第一人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20181130%2Fs00006%2F1543591217580%2F%E3%80%90%E8%BD%89%E6%88%B0%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E3%80%91%E7%82%BA%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%A2%E6%A3%84%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E6%8B%B3%E9%85%AC-%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%98%E5%88%9D%E5%BF%83%E7%88%AD%E5%81%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA&d=OdK%2BOMrWUmYXEJLOqe%2BELdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=cdd5695a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2Farticle%2F20181130%2Fs00006%2F1543591217580%2F%E3%80%90%E8%BD%89%E6%88%B0%E6%A5%AD%E9%A4%98%E3%80%91%E7%82%BA%E5%A5%A7%E9%81%8B%E5%A4%A2%E6%A3%84%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD%E6%8B%B3%E9%85%AC-%E6%9B%B9%E6%98%9F%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%98%E5%88%9D%E5%BF%83%E7%88%AD%E5%81%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA&h=73bab80e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/體育/article/20181130/s00006/1543591217580/【轉戰業餘】為奧運夢棄職業拳酬-曹星如不忘初心爭做香港第一人</a><br />\n<br />\n曹星如在賽後記者會表示，不想再錯過追夢機會，會帶著初心裝備自己，在明年4場計分賽力爭佳績一圓奧運夢，以行動讓其他地方也知道，香港也有拳擊運動員。<br />\n<br />\n曹星如31歲表示，希望在40歲的年齡限制前，一圓夢想：「奧運有年齡限制，自己機會不多了，職業賽反而可以之後再戰。奧運是每個運動員的夢想，很想向外界證明，香港也有拳擊運動員。」"},{"pid":"daaa02ed6ba2a6b2002c8ada560fa1f08f588c66","tid":928392,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:19:56.000Z","msg":"呢條傻鳩幾時先仆街"},{"pid":"7de733505c0400a58075b50c565154f2f7dd619c","tid":928392,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:20:37.000Z","msg":"造賽你就叻，代表香港攞金牌？發夢啦，憑咩 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f36182d5a9fb998456ad16988bfbe574d99486","tid":928392,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:21:47.000Z","msg":"奧運資格賽都唔知出唔出撚到線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505b6fbcd08a858a564f51e0af060a2850b9ca18","tid":928392,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:30:49.000Z","msg":"唔講以為曹星如殺咗樓上三條傻鳩全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2d24254face382949962bdcfbf3ef53a995fe3","tid":928392,"uid":25758,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:33:30.000Z","msg":"人地代表香港都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8989b0a2866199ca0c5dc40ba24673fc5d26bc70","tid":928392,"uid":45925,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"505b6fbcd08a858a564f51e0af060a2850b9ca18","tid":928392,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:30:49.000Z","msg":"唔講以為曹星如殺咗樓上三條傻鳩全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:50:59.000Z","msg":"曹星如 條 marketing team 真係打得出色過佢本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d40cb4b2bb49e746c8fc95e45d9c966f8c505a","tid":928392,"uid":45925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad2d24254face382949962bdcfbf3ef53a995fe3","tid":928392,"uid":25758,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:33:30.000Z","msg":"人地代表香港都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:53:04.000Z","msg":"一句 ：人無恥便無敵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45067fecbed3811bfe4cf95f835cf620d6171a62","tid":928392,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:53:17.000Z","msg":"香港近十年唯一稱得上香港之光嘅人<br />\n好敬佩佢"},{"pid":"07ce6e1e23b5e1f8205b9caefaa52cda5007f744","tid":928392,"uid":45925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45067fecbed3811bfe4cf95f835cf620d6171a62","tid":928392,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T23:53:17.000Z","msg":"香港近十年唯一稱得上香港之光嘅人<br />\n好敬佩佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:03:23.000Z","msg":"到689都未到佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}